flowchart LR
  Prompt[User prompt] --> Runtime[tet_runtime]
  Runtime --> Provider[Provider adapter]
  Provider --> Runtime
  Runtime --> Policy[Tet.Policy]
  Policy --> Tools[Tool executor]
  Tools --> Approval[Approval gate]
  Approval --> Patch[Patch applier]
  Patch --> Verify[Verifier runner]

  Runtime --> Store[(Tet.Store adapter)]
  Tools --> Store
  Approval --> Store
  Patch --> Store
  Verify --> Store

  Store --> Events[Durable Tet.Event timeline]
  Events --> CLI[CLI renderer]
  Events -. optional .-> Web[LiveView renderer]
